{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Two weeks ago I was in my studio in Paris,"},{"time":3000,"text":"and the phone rang and I heard,"},{"time":5000,"text":"\"Hey, JR,"},{"time":7000,"text":"you won the TED Prize 2011."},{"time":9000,"text":"You have to make a wish to save the world.\""},{"time":12000,"text":"I was lost."},{"time":14000,"text":"I mean, I can't save the world. Nobody can."},{"time":17000,"text":"The world is fucked up."},{"time":19000,"text":"Come on, you have dictators ruling the world,"},{"time":21000,"text":"population is growing by millions,"},{"time":23000,"text":"there's no more fish in the sea,"},{"time":25000,"text":"the North Pole is melting"},{"time":27000,"text":"and as the last TED Prize winner said,"},{"time":29000,"text":"we're all becoming fat."},{"time":31000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":33000,"text":"Except maybe French people."},{"time":35000,"text":"Whatever."},{"time":37000,"text":"So I called back"},{"time":39000,"text":"and I told her,"},{"time":41000,"text":"\"Look, Amy,"},{"time":43000,"text":"tell the TED guys I just won't show up."},{"time":45000,"text":"I can't do anything to save the world.\""},{"time":47000,"text":"She said, \"Hey, JR,"},{"time":49000,"text":"your wish is not to save the world, but to change the world.\""},{"time":52000,"text":"\"Oh, all right.\""},{"time":54000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":56000,"text":"\"That's cool.\""},{"time":58000,"text":"I mean, technology, politics, business"},{"time":61000,"text":"do change the world --"},{"time":63000,"text":"not always in a good way, but they do."},{"time":65000,"text":"What about art?"},{"time":67000,"text":"Could art change the world?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71000,"text":"I started when I was 15 years old."},{"time":73000,"text":"And at that time, I was not thinking about changing the world."},{"time":76000,"text":"I was doing graffiti --"},{"time":78000,"text":"writing my name everywhere,"},{"time":80000,"text":"using the city as a canvas."},{"time":84000,"text":"I was going in the tunnels of Paris,"},{"time":86000,"text":"on the rooftops with my friends."},{"time":89000,"text":"Each trip was an excursion,"},{"time":91000,"text":"was an adventure."},{"time":93000,"text":"It was like leaving our mark on society,"},{"time":95000,"text":"to say, \"I was here,\" on the top of a building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"So when I found a cheap camera on the subway,"},{"time":102000,"text":"I started documenting those adventures with my friends"},{"time":106000,"text":"and gave them back as photocopies --"},{"time":109000,"text":"really small photos just that size."},{"time":117000,"text":"That's how, at 17 years old,"},{"time":119000,"text":"I started pasting them."},{"time":121000,"text":"And I did my first \"expo de rue,\""},{"time":123000,"text":"which means sidewalk gallery."},{"time":125000,"text":"And I framed it with color"},{"time":128000,"text":"so you would not confuse it with advertising."},{"time":133000,"text":"I mean, the city's the best gallery I could imagine."},{"time":136000,"text":"I would never have to make a book and then present it to a gallery"},{"time":139000,"text":"and let them decide"},{"time":141000,"text":"if my work was nice enough to show it to people."},{"time":143000,"text":"I would control it directly with the public"},{"time":146000,"text":"in the streets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149000,"text":"So that's Paris."},{"time":151000,"text":"I would change --"},{"time":153000,"text":"depending on the places I would go --"},{"time":155000,"text":"the title of the exhibition."},{"time":157000,"text":"That's on the Champs-Elysees."},{"time":159000,"text":"I was quite proud of that one."},{"time":161000,"text":"Because I was just 18"},{"time":163000,"text":"and I was just up there on the top of the Champs-Elysees."},{"time":165000,"text":"Then when the photo left,"},{"time":167000,"text":"the frame was still there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":171000,"text":"November 2005:"},{"time":173000,"text":"the streets are burning."},{"time":175000,"text":"A large wave of riots"},{"time":177000,"text":"had broken into the first projects of Paris."},{"time":181000,"text":"Everyone was glued to the TV,"},{"time":183000,"text":"watching disturbing, frightening images"},{"time":187000,"text":"taken from the edge of the neighborhood."},{"time":191000,"text":"I mean, these kids, without control,"},{"time":194000,"text":"throwing Molotov cocktails,"},{"time":196000,"text":"attacking the cops and the firemen,"},{"time":198000,"text":"looting everything they could in the shops."},{"time":200000,"text":"These were criminals, thugs, dangerous,"},{"time":203000,"text":"destroying their own environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206000,"text":"And then I saw it -- could it be possible? --"},{"time":209000,"text":"my photo on a wall"},{"time":212000,"text":"revealed by a burning car --"},{"time":215000,"text":"a pasting I'd done a year earlier --"},{"time":217000,"text":"an illegal one -- still there."},{"time":220000,"text":"I mean, these were the faces of my friends."},{"time":222000,"text":"I know those guys."},{"time":224000,"text":"All of them are not angels,"},{"time":226000,"text":"but they're not monsters either."},{"time":230000,"text":"So it was kind of weird to see"},{"time":232000,"text":"those images and those eyes stare back at me through a television."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236000,"text":"So I went back there"},{"time":238000,"text":"with a 28 mm lens."},{"time":241000,"text":"It was the only one I had at that time."},{"time":243000,"text":"But with that lens,"},{"time":245000,"text":"you have to be as close as 10 inches from the person."},{"time":248000,"text":"So you can do it only with their trust."},{"time":251000,"text":"So I took full portraits of people from Le Bosquet."},{"time":255000,"text":"They were making scary faces"},{"time":257000,"text":"to play the caricature of themselves."},{"time":272000,"text":"And then I pasted huge posters everywhere"},{"time":275000,"text":"in the bourgeois area of Paris"},{"time":277000,"text":"with the name, age, even building number"},{"time":280000,"text":"of these guys."},{"time":289000,"text":"A year later,"},{"time":291000,"text":"the exhibition was displayed in front of the city hall of Paris."},{"time":294000,"text":"And we go from thug images,"},{"time":297000,"text":"who've been stolen and distorted by the media,"},{"time":300000,"text":"who's now proudly taking over his own image."},{"time":303000,"text":"That's where I realized"},{"time":305000,"text":"the power of paper and glue."},{"time":315000,"text":"So could art change the world?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":318000,"text":"A year later,"},{"time":320000,"text":"I was listening to all the noise"},{"time":322000,"text":"about the Middle East conflict."},{"time":324000,"text":"I mean, at that time, trust me,"},{"time":326000,"text":"they were only referring to the Israeli and Palestinian conflict."},{"time":328000,"text":"So with my friend Marco,"},{"time":330000,"text":"we decided to go there"},{"time":332000,"text":"and see who are the real Palestinians and who are the real Israelis."},{"time":335000,"text":"Are they so different?"},{"time":337000,"text":"When we got there, we just went in the street,"},{"time":340000,"text":"started talking with people everywhere,"},{"time":343000,"text":"and we realized that things were a bit different"},{"time":345000,"text":"from the rhetoric we heard in the media."},{"time":348000,"text":"So we decided to take portraits"},{"time":350000,"text":"of Palestinians and Israelis"},{"time":352000,"text":"doing the same jobs --"},{"time":354000,"text":"taxi-driver, lawyer, cooks."},{"time":358000,"text":"Asked them to make a face as a sign of commitment."},{"time":361000,"text":"Not a smile -- that really doesn't tell"},{"time":363000,"text":"about who you are and what you feel."},{"time":365000,"text":"They all accepted"},{"time":367000,"text":"to be pasted next to the other."},{"time":370000,"text":"I decided to paste"},{"time":372000,"text":"in eight Israeli and Palestinian cities"},{"time":376000,"text":"and on both sides of the wall."},{"time":379000,"text":"We launched the biggest illegal art exhibition ever."},{"time":382000,"text":"We called the project Face 2 Face."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385000,"text":"The experts said, \"No way."},{"time":388000,"text":"The people will not accept."},{"time":391000,"text":"The army will shoot you, and Hamas will kidnap you.\""},{"time":393000,"text":"We said, \"Okay, let's try and push as far as we can.\""},{"time":397000,"text":"I love the way that people will ask me,"},{"time":399000,"text":"\"How big will my photo be?\""},{"time":401000,"text":"\"It will be as big as your house.\""},{"time":404000,"text":"When we did the wall, we did the Palestinian side."},{"time":407000,"text":"So we arrived with just our ladders"},{"time":409000,"text":"and we realized that they were not high enough."},{"time":411000,"text":"And so Palestinians guys say,"},{"time":413000,"text":"\"Calm down. No wait. I'm going to find you a solution.\""},{"time":416000,"text":"So he went to the Church of Nativity"},{"time":419000,"text":"and brought back an old ladder"},{"time":421000,"text":"that was so old that it could have seen Jesus being born."},{"time":424000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":426000,"text":"We did Face 2 Face with only six friends,"},{"time":429000,"text":"two ladders, two brushes,"},{"time":432000,"text":"a rented car, a camera"},{"time":434000,"text":"and 20,000 square feet of paper."},{"time":437000,"text":"We had all sorts of help"},{"time":439000,"text":"from all walks of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444000,"text":"Okay, for example, that's Palestine."},{"time":446000,"text":"We're in Ramallah right now."},{"time":448000,"text":"We're pasting portraits --"},{"time":450000,"text":"so both portraits in the streets in a crowded market."},{"time":452000,"text":"People come around us and start asking,"},{"time":455000,"text":"\"What are you doing here?\""},{"time":457000,"text":"\"Oh, we're actually doing an art project"},{"time":459000,"text":"and we are pasting an Israeli and a Palestinian doing the same job."},{"time":462000,"text":"And those ones are actually two taxi-drivers.\""},{"time":465000,"text":"And then there was always a silence."},{"time":468000,"text":"\"You mean you're pasting an Israeli face --"},{"time":471000,"text":"doing a face -- right here?\""},{"time":473000,"text":"\"Well, yeah, yeah, that's part of the project.\""},{"time":476000,"text":"And I would always leave that moment,"},{"time":478000,"text":"and we would ask them,"},{"time":480000,"text":"\"So can you tell me who is who?\""},{"time":483000,"text":"And most of them couldn't say."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"We even pasted on Israeli military towers,"},{"time":494000,"text":"and nothing happened."},{"time":496000,"text":"When you paste an image, it's just paper and glue."},{"time":499000,"text":"People can tear it, tag on it, or even pee on it --"},{"time":502000,"text":"some are a bit high for that, I agree --"},{"time":504000,"text":"but the people in the street,"},{"time":506000,"text":"they are the curator."},{"time":508000,"text":"The rain and the wind will take them off anyway."},{"time":510000,"text":"They are not meant to stay."},{"time":512000,"text":"But exactly four years after,"},{"time":515000,"text":"the photos, most of them are still there."},{"time":518000,"text":"Face 2 Face demonstrated"},{"time":520000,"text":"that what we thought impossible was possible --"},{"time":523000,"text":"and, you know what, even easy."},{"time":525000,"text":"We didn't push the limit;"},{"time":527000,"text":"we just showed that they were further than anyone thought."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532000,"text":"In the Middle East, I experienced my work"},{"time":534000,"text":"in places without [many] museums."},{"time":536000,"text":"So the reactions in the street"},{"time":539000,"text":"were kind of interesting."},{"time":541000,"text":"So I decided to go further in this direction"},{"time":543000,"text":"and go in places where there were zero museums."},{"time":549000,"text":"When you go in these developing societies,"},{"time":552000,"text":"women are the pillars of their community,"},{"time":555000,"text":"but the men are still the ones holding the streets."},{"time":558000,"text":"So we were inspired to create a project"},{"time":561000,"text":"where men will pay tribute to women"},{"time":564000,"text":"by posting their photos."},{"time":567000,"text":"I called that project Women Are Heroes."},{"time":571000,"text":"When I listened to all the stories"},{"time":573000,"text":"everywhere I went on the continents,"},{"time":575000,"text":"I couldn't always understand"},{"time":577000,"text":"the complicated circumstances of their conflict."},{"time":580000,"text":"I just observed."},{"time":583000,"text":"Sometimes there was no words,"},{"time":586000,"text":"no sentence, just tears."},{"time":589000,"text":"I just took their pictures"},{"time":592000,"text":"and pasted them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596000,"text":"Women Are Heroes took me around the world."},{"time":599000,"text":"Most of the places I went to,"},{"time":601000,"text":"I decided to go there"},{"time":603000,"text":"because I've heard about it through the media."},{"time":605000,"text":"So for example, in June 2008,"},{"time":607000,"text":"I was watching TV in Paris,"},{"time":609000,"text":"and then I heard about this terrible thing"},{"time":611000,"text":"that happened in Rio de Janeiro --"},{"time":613000,"text":"the first favela of Brazil named Providencia."},{"time":617000,"text":"Three kids -- that was three students --"},{"time":620000,"text":"were [detained] by the army"},{"time":622000,"text":"because they were not carrying their papers."},{"time":624000,"text":"And the army took them,"},{"time":626000,"text":"and instead of bringing them to the police station,"},{"time":629000,"text":"they brought them to an enemy favela"},{"time":632000,"text":"where they get chopped into pieces."},{"time":634000,"text":"I was shocked."},{"time":636000,"text":"All Brazil was shocked."},{"time":638000,"text":"I heard it was one of the most violent favelas,"},{"time":641000,"text":"because the largest drug cartel controls it."},{"time":644000,"text":"So I decided to go there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":646000,"text":"When I arrived --"},{"time":648000,"text":"I mean, I didn't have any contact with any NGO."},{"time":651000,"text":"There was none in place -- no association, no NGOs, nothing --"},{"time":654000,"text":"no eyewitnesses."},{"time":656000,"text":"So we just walked around,"},{"time":658000,"text":"and we met a woman,"},{"time":660000,"text":"and I showed her my book."},{"time":662000,"text":"And she said, \"You know what?"},{"time":664000,"text":"We're hungry for culture."},{"time":666000,"text":"We need culture out there.\""},{"time":669000,"text":"So I went out and I started with the kids."},{"time":672000,"text":"I just took a few photos of the kids,"},{"time":674000,"text":"and the next day I came with the posters and we pasted them."},{"time":677000,"text":"The day after, I came back and they were already scratched."},{"time":680000,"text":"But that's okay."},{"time":682000,"text":"I wanted them to feel that this art belongs to them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686000,"text":"Then the next day, I held a meeting on the main square"},{"time":689000,"text":"and some women came."},{"time":691000,"text":"They were all linked to the three kids that got killed."},{"time":696000,"text":"There was the mother, the grandmother, the best friend --"},{"time":699000,"text":"they all wanted to shout the story."},{"time":703000,"text":"After that day,"},{"time":705000,"text":"everyone in the favela gave me the green light."},{"time":708000,"text":"I took more photos, and we started the project."},{"time":711000,"text":"The drug lords were kind of worried"},{"time":713000,"text":"about us filming in the place,"},{"time":715000,"text":"so I told them, \"You know what?"},{"time":717000,"text":"I'm not interested in filming the violence and the weapons."},{"time":719000,"text":"You see that enough in the media."},{"time":721000,"text":"What I want to show is the incredible life and energy."},{"time":723000,"text":"I've been seeing it around me the last few days.\""},{"time":727000,"text":"So that's a really symbolic pasting,"},{"time":729000,"text":"because that's the first one we did that you couldn't see from the city."},{"time":732000,"text":"And that's where the three kids got arrested,"},{"time":735000,"text":"and that's the grandmother of one of them."},{"time":738000,"text":"And on that stairs,"},{"time":740000,"text":"that's where the traffickers always stand"},{"time":742000,"text":"and there's a lot of exchange of fire."},{"time":744000,"text":"Everyone there understood the project."},{"time":748000,"text":"And then we pasted everywhere -- the whole hill."}]},{"cues":[{"time":751000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":761000,"text":"What was interesting is that the media couldn't get in."},{"time":763000,"text":"I mean, you should see that."},{"time":765000,"text":"They would have to film us from a really long distance by helicopter"},{"time":768000,"text":"and then have a really long lens,"},{"time":770000,"text":"and we would see ourselves, on TV, pasting."},{"time":772000,"text":"And they would put a number: \"Please call this number"},{"time":774000,"text":"if you know what's going on in Providencia.\""},{"time":776000,"text":"We just did a project and then left"},{"time":779000,"text":"so the media wouldn't know."},{"time":781000,"text":"So how can we know about the project?"},{"time":783000,"text":"So they had to go and find the women"},{"time":786000,"text":"and get an explanation from them."},{"time":788000,"text":"So you create a bridge between the media"},{"time":791000,"text":"and the anonymous women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794000,"text":"We kept traveling."},{"time":796000,"text":"We went to Africa, Sudan, Sierra Leone,"},{"time":798000,"text":"Liberia, Kenya."},{"time":800000,"text":"In war-torn places like Monrovia,"},{"time":802000,"text":"people come straight to you."},{"time":804000,"text":"I mean, they want to know what you're up to."},{"time":806000,"text":"They kept asking me, \"What is the purpose of your project?"},{"time":809000,"text":"Are you an NGO? Are you the media?\""},{"time":812000,"text":"Art. Just doing art."},{"time":815000,"text":"Some people question, \"Why is it in black and white?"},{"time":817000,"text":"Don't you have color in France?\""},{"time":819000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":821000,"text":"Or they tell you, \"Are these people all dead?\""},{"time":823000,"text":"Some who understood the project would explain it to others."},{"time":826000,"text":"And to a man who did not understand, I heard someone say,"},{"time":829000,"text":"\"You know, you've been here for a few hours"},{"time":832000,"text":"trying to understand, discussing with your fellows."},{"time":835000,"text":"During that time, you haven't thought about"},{"time":837000,"text":"what you're going to eat tomorrow."},{"time":839000,"text":"This is art.\""},{"time":842000,"text":"I think it's people's curiosity"},{"time":845000,"text":"that motivates them"},{"time":848000,"text":"to come into the projects."},{"time":850000,"text":"And then it becomes more."},{"time":852000,"text":"It becomes a desire, a need, an armor."},{"time":856000,"text":"On this bridge that's in Monrovia,"},{"time":859000,"text":"ex-rebel soldiers helped us pasting a portrait"},{"time":862000,"text":"of a woman that might have been raped during the war."},{"time":865000,"text":"Women are always the first ones targeted"},{"time":867000,"text":"during conflict."}]},{"cues":[{"time":870000,"text":"This is Kibera, Kenya,"},{"time":872000,"text":"one of the largest slums of Africa."},{"time":875000,"text":"You might have seen images about the post-election violence"},{"time":878000,"text":"that happened there in 2008."},{"time":882000,"text":"This time we covered the roofs of the houses,"},{"time":884000,"text":"but we didn't use paper,"},{"time":887000,"text":"because paper doesn't prevent the rain"},{"time":890000,"text":"from leaking inside the house --"},{"time":892000,"text":"vinyl does."},{"time":894000,"text":"Then art becomes useful."},{"time":896000,"text":"So the people kept it."},{"time":898000,"text":"You know what I love is, for example, when you see the biggest eye there,"},{"time":901000,"text":"there are so [many] houses inside."},{"time":903000,"text":"And I went there a few months ago --"},{"time":905000,"text":"photos are still there -- and it was missing a piece of the eye."},{"time":908000,"text":"So I asked the people what happened."},{"time":910000,"text":"\"Oh, that guy just moved.\""},{"time":912000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":916000,"text":"When the roofs were covered, a woman said as a joke,"},{"time":919000,"text":"\"Now God can see me.\""},{"time":921000,"text":"When you look at Kibera now,"},{"time":923000,"text":"they look back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":929000,"text":"Okay, India."},{"time":931000,"text":"Before I start that, just so you know,"},{"time":933000,"text":"each time we go to a place, we don't have authorization,"},{"time":935000,"text":"so we set up like commandos --"},{"time":937000,"text":"we're a group of friends who arrive there,"},{"time":939000,"text":"and we try to paste on the walls."},{"time":941000,"text":"But there are places where you just can't paste on a wall."},{"time":944000,"text":"In India it was just impossible to paste."},{"time":947000,"text":"I heard culturally and because of the law,"},{"time":950000,"text":"they would just arrest us at the first pasting."},{"time":953000,"text":"So we decided to paste white,"},{"time":955000,"text":"white on the walls."},{"time":957000,"text":"So imagine white guys pasting white papers."},{"time":959000,"text":"So people would come to us and ask us,"},{"time":961000,"text":"\"Hey, what are you up to?\""},{"time":963000,"text":"\"Oh, you know, we're just doing art.\" \"Art?\""},{"time":967000,"text":"Of course, they were confused."},{"time":969000,"text":"But you know how India has a lot of dust in the streets,"},{"time":972000,"text":"and the more dust you would have"},{"time":974000,"text":"going up in the air,"},{"time":976000,"text":"on the white paper you can almost see,"},{"time":979000,"text":"but there is this sticky part"},{"time":981000,"text":"like when you reverse a sticker."},{"time":983000,"text":"So the more dust you have, the more it will reveal the photo."},{"time":986000,"text":"So we could just walk in the street during the next days"},{"time":989000,"text":"and the photos would get revealed by themselves."},{"time":991000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":998000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":1001000,"text":"So we didn't get caught this time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1006000,"text":"Each project -- that's a film"},{"time":1008000,"text":"from Women Are Heroes."},{"time":1011000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":1014000,"text":"Okay."},{"time":1016000,"text":"For each project we do"},{"time":1018000,"text":"a film."},{"time":1020000,"text":"And most of what you see -- that's a trailer from \"Women Are Heroes\" --"},{"time":1023000,"text":"its images, photography,"},{"time":1026000,"text":"taken one after the other."},{"time":1047000,"text":"And the photos kept traveling even without us."},{"time":1086000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1088000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1098000,"text":"Hopefully, you'll see the film,"},{"time":1100000,"text":"and you'll understand the scope of the project"},{"time":1102000,"text":"and what the people felt when they saw those photos."},{"time":1104000,"text":"Because that's a big part of it. There's layers behind each photo."},{"time":1107000,"text":"Behind each image is a story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1110000,"text":"Women Are Heroes created a new dynamic"},{"time":1112000,"text":"in each of the communities,"},{"time":1114000,"text":"and the women kept that dynamic after we left."},{"time":1117000,"text":"For example, we did books -- not for sale --"},{"time":1120000,"text":"that all the community would get."},{"time":1122000,"text":"But to get it, they would have to [get] it signed by one of the women."},{"time":1126000,"text":"We did that in most of the places."},{"time":1128000,"text":"We go back regularly."},{"time":1130000,"text":"And so in Providencia, for example, in the favela,"},{"time":1133000,"text":"we have a cultural center running there."},{"time":1135000,"text":"In Kibera, each year we cover more roofs."},{"time":1137000,"text":"Because of course, when we left, the people who were just at the edge of the project"},{"time":1140000,"text":"said, \"Hey, what about my roof?\""},{"time":1143000,"text":"So we decided to come the year after"},{"time":1145000,"text":"and keep doing the project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1148000,"text":"A really important point for me"},{"time":1150000,"text":"is that I don't use any brand or corporate sponsors."},{"time":1153000,"text":"So I have no responsibility"},{"time":1155000,"text":"to anyone but myself"},{"time":1157000,"text":"and the subjects."},{"time":1159000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1163000,"text":"And that is for me"},{"time":1165000,"text":"one of the more important things in the work."},{"time":1167000,"text":"I think, today,"},{"time":1169000,"text":"as important as the result is the way you do things."},{"time":1172000,"text":"And that has always been a central part of the work."},{"time":1176000,"text":"And what's interesting is that fine line that I have"},{"time":1178000,"text":"with images and advertising."},{"time":1180000,"text":"We just did some pasting in Los Angeles"},{"time":1182000,"text":"on another project in the last weeks."},{"time":1185000,"text":"And I was even invited to cover the MOCA museum."},{"time":1189000,"text":"But yesterday the city called them and said,"},{"time":1191000,"text":"\"Look, you're going to have to tear it down."},{"time":1193000,"text":"Because this can be taken for advertising,"},{"time":1195000,"text":"and because of the law,"},{"time":1197000,"text":"it has to be taken down.\""},{"time":1199000,"text":"But tell me, advertising for what?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1202000,"text":"The people I photograph"},{"time":1204000,"text":"were proud to participate in the project"},{"time":1206000,"text":"and to have their photo in the community."},{"time":1208000,"text":"But they asked me for a promise basically."},{"time":1210000,"text":"They asked me, \"Please, make our story travel with you.\""},{"time":1214000,"text":"So I did. That's Paris."},{"time":1217000,"text":"That's Rio."},{"time":1219000,"text":"In each place, we built exhibitions with a story, and the story traveled."},{"time":1223000,"text":"You understand the full scope of the project."},{"time":1225000,"text":"That's London."},{"time":1228000,"text":"New York."},{"time":1230000,"text":"And today, they are with you in Long Beach."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1234000,"text":"All right, recently I started a public art project"},{"time":1237000,"text":"where I don't use my artwork anymore."},{"time":1240000,"text":"I use Man Ray, Helen Levitt,"},{"time":1243000,"text":"Giacomelli, other people's artwork."},{"time":1245000,"text":"It doesn't matter today if it's your photo or not."},{"time":1248000,"text":"The importance is what you do"},{"time":1250000,"text":"with the images,"},{"time":1252000,"text":"the statement it makes where it's pasted."},{"time":1255000,"text":"So for example, I pasted the photo of the minaret"},{"time":1258000,"text":"in Switzerland"},{"time":1260000,"text":"a few weeks after they voted the law forbidding minarets in the country."},{"time":1264000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1270000,"text":"This image of three men wearing gas masks"},{"time":1273000,"text":"was taken in Chernobyl originally,"},{"time":1275000,"text":"and I pasted it in Southern Italy,"},{"time":1278000,"text":"where the mafia sometimes bury the garbage under the ground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1284000,"text":"In some ways, art can change the world."},{"time":1286000,"text":"Art is not supposed to change the world,"},{"time":1288000,"text":"to change practical things,"},{"time":1290000,"text":"but to change perceptions."},{"time":1292000,"text":"Art can change"},{"time":1294000,"text":"the way we see the world."},{"time":1296000,"text":"Art can create an analogy."},{"time":1299000,"text":"Actually the fact that art cannot change things"},{"time":1302000,"text":"makes it a neutral place"},{"time":1304000,"text":"for exchanges and discussions,"},{"time":1307000,"text":"and then enables you to change the world."},{"time":1310000,"text":"When I do my work,"},{"time":1312000,"text":"I have two kinds of reactions."},{"time":1314000,"text":"People say, \"Oh, why don't you go in Iraq or Afghanistan."},{"time":1317000,"text":"They would be really useful.\""},{"time":1319000,"text":"Or, \"How can we help?\""},{"time":1322000,"text":"I presume that you belong to the second category,"},{"time":1325000,"text":"and that's good,"},{"time":1327000,"text":"because for that project,"},{"time":1329000,"text":"I'm going to ask you to take the photos"},{"time":1331000,"text":"and paste them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1334000,"text":"So now my wish is:"},{"time":1336000,"text":"(mock drum roll)"},{"time":1338000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1341000,"text":"I wish for you to stand up"},{"time":1344000,"text":"for what you care about"},{"time":1347000,"text":"by participating in a global art project,"},{"time":1350000,"text":"and together we'll turn the world inside out."},{"time":1356000,"text":"And this starts right now."},{"time":1358000,"text":"Yes, everyone in the room."},{"time":1360000,"text":"Everyone watching."},{"time":1363000,"text":"I wanted that wish"},{"time":1365000,"text":"to actually start now."},{"time":1367000,"text":"So a subject you're passionate about, a person who you want to tell their story"},{"time":1370000,"text":"or even your own photos --"},{"time":1372000,"text":"tell me what you stand for."},{"time":1374000,"text":"Take the photos, the portraits,"},{"time":1376000,"text":"upload it -- I'll give you all the details --"},{"time":1379000,"text":"and I'll send you back your poster. Join by groups"},{"time":1382000,"text":"and reveal things to the world."},{"time":1385000,"text":"The full data is on the website --"},{"time":1388000,"text":"insideoutproject.net --"},{"time":1390000,"text":"that is launching today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1393000,"text":"What we see changes who we are."},{"time":1395000,"text":"When we act together,"},{"time":1397000,"text":"the whole thing is much more than the sum of the parts."},{"time":1401000,"text":"So I hope that, together, we'll create something"},{"time":1403000,"text":"that the world will remember."},{"time":1405000,"text":"And this starts right now and depends on you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1408000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1410000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1417000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1419000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}